Hello,
for my Xamarin.iOS project I was using this code to save data as JPG whit SkiaSharp 1.56.2:
```
SKImage image = SKImage.FromBitmap(pageBitmap);
SKData data = image.Encode(SKImageEncodeFormat.Jpeg, 100);
```

When I upgrade to SkiaSharp 1.57.0 and update code like that:
```
SKImage image = SKImage.FromBitmap(pageBitmap);
SKData data = image.Encode(SKEncodedImageFormat.Jpeg, 100);
```

Data are always null. When I downgrade to SkiaSharp 1.56.2 it starts working again.
